      "instruction": "<p>Slice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into rounds</p><p>Wash your<strong> lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Remove the <strong>outer leaves</strong> and set aside, then shred the <strong>inner core</strong></p>",
